# 🔒 MindKraft (Vox) — Security Audit & Hardening Plan

## Executive Summary

The application has **15+ critical/high vulnerabilities** that can be exploited to bypass auth, access admin APIs without credentials, extract student data, spoof face recognition, and perform injection attacks. This plan prioritizes fixes by exploitability.

---

## Current Security Posture

| Area | Status | Grade |
|------|--------|-------|
| Admin Auth (V1 JWT) | JWT-protected, bcrypt hashing | 🟡 B |
| Admin Auth (Legacy) | **No JWT, no session — completely open** | 🔴 F |
| Student Auth | **Client-side sessionStorage only** | 🔴 F |
| API Authorization | **30+ admin routes have zero auth** | 🔴 F |
| Rate Limiting | **None** | 🔴 F |
| Input Validation | **No sanitization, raw dict bodies** | 🔴 F |
