## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Backend Authentication Hardening

---

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///d:/mindkraft/Team-A-Frontend/Team-A-Backend/Team-A-Backend/app/main.py)

- **Fix VULN-01:** Add JWT middleware to ALL `/api/admin/*` legacy routes via a `Depends(require_admin_jwt)` dependency
- **Fix VULN-04:** Replace raw `dict[str, Any]` bodies with Pydantic models for input validation and block MongoDB operators
- **Fix VULN-05:** Sanitize generic exception handler — log full error server-side, return generic message to client
- **Fix VULN-10:** Make `/api/admin/login` return a JWT token (same as V1 login does)
- **Fix VULN-15:** Add JWT dependency to student exam endpoints

#### [MODIFY] [security.py](file:///d:/mindkraft/Team-A-Frontend/Team-A-Backend/Team-A-Backend/app/security.py)

- **Fix VULN-02:** Remove plaintext password fallback — only accept bcrypt hashes
- Add `require_admin_jwt` dependency function for legacy routes
- Add `require_student_jwt` dependency function

#### [NEW] `app/middleware/rate_limiter.py`

- **Fix VULN-06:** Add rate limiting middleware:
  - Login endpoints: 5 attempts per 15 minutes per IP
  - Face verification: 10 attempts per 15 minutes per IP
  - General API: 100 requests per minute per IP

#### [NEW] `app/models/` (Pydantic request models)

- **Fix VULN-04:** Define strict Pydantic models for all request bodies
- Validates types, rejects MongoDB operators like `$gt`, `$ne`

---

### Component 2: Face Auth Hardening

---

#### [MODIFY] [face.py](file:///d:/mindkraft/Team-A-Frontend/Team-A-Backend/Team-A-Backend/app/services/face.py)

- **Fix VULN-07:** Restore thresholds to `0.85` cosine / `0.55` euclidean, use AND instead of OR
- **Fix VULN-08:** Add server-side liveness score check (require multiple frame descriptors with variance)
- Add embedding dimension validation (reject if not exactly 128D)
- Encrypt embeddings at rest using field-level encryption

